WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:03.750
Well, good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:03.760 --> 00:00:05.910
joining us again tonight. It's Brandon

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:08.710
and Diana, the

00:00:08.720 --> 00:00:11.830
Dynamic Duo. We're here and we're ready

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:14.230
to pray.

00:00:14.240 --> 00:00:15.910
We've been seeking the Lord today

00:00:15.920 --> 00:00:18.390
and praying over our nation because of

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.390
all that happened today. The Lord

00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:23.109
has been warning us that this was

00:00:23.119 --> 00:00:26.790
going to take place. We pray for

00:00:26.800 --> 00:00:28.550
the troops,

00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:30.710
the two victims who are fighting for

00:00:30.720 --> 00:00:31.990
their lives right now. I don't know if

00:00:32.000 --> 00:00:33.430
they're still alive or

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:35.590
still fighting, but we know that God is

00:00:35.600 --> 00:00:37.670
able, and we're going to pray for

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:38.950
them right now. We're going to pray for

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.790
their families and pray

00:00:40.800 --> 00:00:43.190
peace over them, that God would

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.270
restore their health and that this

00:00:45.280 --> 00:00:48.229
heinous act will be punished

00:00:48.239 --> 00:00:52.310
quickly. What the

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:54.630
devil meant for bad, God's going to turn

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:57.670
around and get the glory for it. I

00:00:57.680 --> 00:00:59.110
believe with all my heart that's

00:00:59.120 --> 00:01:03.590
what we're here for.

00:01:03.600 --> 00:01:06.710
As I was praying this afternoon,

00:01:06.720 --> 00:01:08.870
I was caught up.

00:01:08.880 --> 00:01:11.270
He spoke about Saturday; we were praying over

00:01:11.280 --> 00:01:13.429
Saturday and the 14

00:01:13.439 --> 00:01:16.469
people. There are other

00:01:16.479 --> 00:01:18.950
events, and the Lord said, 'This is what

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:21.830
I warned you about. These are the things

00:01:21.840 --> 00:01:24.230
that I'm warning you

00:01:24.230 --> 00:01:24.240
about.'It's

00:01:24.240 --> 00:01:26.630
underground chatter,

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:28.310
and the Lord specifically brought this

00:01:28.320 --> 00:01:30.230
up today. He said, 'The underground

00:01:30.240 --> 00:01:35.190
chatter, son, for more acts to come.'We

00:01:35.190 --> 00:01:35.200
are

00:01:35.200 --> 00:01:38.710
praying against the acts to come over

00:01:38.720 --> 00:01:40.789
our malls

00:01:40.799 --> 00:01:42.310
specifically,

00:01:42.320 --> 00:01:45.429
and the tree-lighting ceremonies

00:01:45.429 --> 00:01:45.439
and

00:01:45.439 --> 00:01:46.950
drones.

00:01:46.960 --> 00:01:49.429
They have brought forth this one

00:01:49.439 --> 00:01:51.990
act,

00:01:51.990 --> 00:01:52.000
and

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:54.469
you'll hear in just a second more

00:01:54.479 --> 00:01:56.069
about what's going to happen because of

00:01:56.079 --> 00:01:57.910
the act that happened today. We pray.

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:00.389
This was right by the White House, and

00:02:00.399 --> 00:02:02.469
President Trump wasn't there, thank God.

00:02:02.479 --> 00:02:07.030
He was at Mar-a-Lago, and we

00:02:07.040 --> 00:02:08.630
continued to pray for him and for

00:02:08.640 --> 00:02:11.029
Vice President

00:02:15.430 --> 00:02:15.440
Vance.

00:02:18.239 --> 00:02:20.309
I keep forgetting;

00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:21.830
you'll have to bear with

00:02:21.840 --> 00:02:23.750
me.

00:02:23.760 --> 00:02:26.229
We pray for JD Vance.

00:02:31.440 --> 00:02:34.229
I

00:02:34.239 --> 00:02:36.869
know what the Lord is warning me about,

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:39.350
and he keeps bringing up

00:02:39.360 --> 00:02:43.030
that in the

00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:46.710
days ahead, they will challenge the peace

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:49.589
that you have every single day

00:02:49.589 --> 00:02:49.599
as

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:52.070
you go about your normal life. The

00:02:52.080 --> 00:02:55.030
enemy would try to challenge that

00:02:55.030 --> 00:02:55.040
so

00:02:55.040 --> 00:02:58.070
you live in fear and question

00:02:58.080 --> 00:03:00.390
everything: 'Is it okay to go here? Is it

00:03:00.400 --> 00:03:03.190
okay to go there?'We take for granted as

00:03:03.200 --> 00:03:06.710
United States citizens the great job our

00:03:06.720 --> 00:03:09.509
law enforcement does every single day.

00:03:09.519 --> 00:03:11.910
Our FBI, our Homeland Security, our

00:03:11.920 --> 00:03:13.670
local law enforcement, and our sheriff's

00:03:13.670 --> 00:03:13.680
departments

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:17.589
are always out to

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:20.070
protect and serve our

00:03:20.080 --> 00:03:22.550
beautiful nation. The enemy

00:03:22.560 --> 00:03:25.750
would try to challenge our way of life

00:03:25.750 --> 00:03:25.760
so

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:29.430
that you would feel that insecurity

00:03:29.440 --> 00:03:32.470
of whether we are safe to go to the mall.

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:34.309
That was what the Lord

00:03:34.319 --> 00:03:36.229
was showing me: the enemy

00:03:36.239 --> 00:03:41.030
was going to try to instill fear,

00:03:41.040 --> 00:03:44.550
worry, panic, and dread.

00:03:46.239 --> 00:03:48.710
As I was praying over that today, I

00:03:48.720 --> 00:03:51.990
kept praying into Saturday

00:03:51.990 --> 00:03:52.000
tree-lighting

00:03:52.000 --> 00:03:54.229
ceremonies and massive get-togethers

00:03:54.239 --> 00:03:57.750
tomorrow for the parade, praying over New

00:03:57.760 --> 00:04:01.509
York,

00:04:01.519 --> 00:04:08.309
Las Vegas,

00:04:08.319 --> 00:04:12.309
our airports, our TSA, and

00:04:12.309 --> 00:04:12.319
those who

00:04:12.319 --> 00:04:15.270
check the

00:04:15.280 --> 00:04:18.390
baggage. We pray that

00:04:18.400 --> 00:04:20.629
God would always intervene, that there

00:04:20.639 --> 00:04:22.629
would be supernatural divine

00:04:22.639 --> 00:04:25.990
intervention for our nation. That's

00:04:26.000 --> 00:04:27.670
what we'll continue to pray

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:29.350
about tonight. That is what I feel in my

00:04:29.360 --> 00:04:30.790
heart the Lord is wanting us to

00:04:30.800 --> 00:04:32.950
keep interceding for.

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:36.310
Like I said,

00:04:36.320 --> 00:04:37.909
stuff like this shouldn't

00:04:37.919 --> 00:04:41.030
happen.

00:04:41.040 --> 00:04:42.950
The

00:04:44.790 --> 00:04:44.800
fact

00:04:47.280 --> 00:04:50.550
that two troops got

00:04:50.560 --> 00:04:53.030
almost fatally shot so far

00:04:53.030 --> 00:04:53.040
is

00:04:53.040 --> 00:04:55.510
ridiculous. I wanted to say

00:04:58.479 --> 00:05:00.390
everything is at peace,

00:05:02.560 --> 00:05:03.749
but

00:05:03.759 --> 00:05:05.270
we live in a fallen

00:05:05.280 --> 00:05:06.710
world and

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:08.070
things sometimes slip through the

00:05:08.080 --> 00:05:09.909
cracks. We're going to stand

00:05:09.919 --> 00:05:11.430
on the blood

00:05:11.430 --> 00:05:11.440
and

00:05:11.440 --> 00:05:12.710
our covenant tonight,

00:05:12.710 --> 00:05:12.720
believing

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.230
God

00:05:17.280 --> 00:05:19.029
for the holiday season.

00:05:19.039 --> 00:05:23.510
In particular, the Lord said

00:05:23.520 --> 00:05:26.550
Thursday, Friday, and Saturday

00:05:26.550 --> 00:05:26.560
are

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:28.870
three major days.

00:05:28.880 --> 00:05:34.150
We have work to do, and I

00:05:34.160 --> 00:05:35.430
believe many people are

00:05:35.440 --> 00:05:37.909
up for the task. There are 2,000 of you

00:05:37.909 --> 00:05:37.919
here

00:05:37.919 --> 00:05:39.350
already;

00:05:39.360 --> 00:05:41.029
you

00:05:41.039 --> 00:05:43.350
know the seriousness of the hour.

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:44.710
Some of you don't even live in

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:47.029
America, but this was not concerning

00:05:47.039 --> 00:05:50.150
just America. The Lord said, 'You must

00:05:50.160 --> 00:05:53.029
pray for France,

00:05:53.039 --> 00:05:56.629
Germany, and all

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:58.550
of

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:01.029
Europe.'Praying

00:06:01.039 --> 00:06:04.230
for

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:05.990
Australia,

00:06:06.000 --> 00:06:08.469
New Zealand, and

00:06:08.469 --> 00:06:08.479
so on.

00:06:08.479 --> 00:06:10.390
It's interesting—I didn't feel

00:06:10.390 --> 00:06:10.400
led

00:06:10.400 --> 00:06:12.870
to pray concerning these

00:06:12.880 --> 00:06:15.670
terrorist attacks for any

00:06:15.670 --> 00:06:15.680
Asian

00:06:15.680 --> 00:06:18.390
nations; it's always the

00:06:18.400 --> 00:06:22.309
Western nations like Europe and Canada.

00:06:22.319 --> 00:06:24.790
We'll just do our job. I want to

00:06:24.800 --> 00:06:27.029
play this video if you're not familiar

00:06:27.039 --> 00:06:29.909
with today's events.

00:06:35.360 --> 00:06:39.110
Pete is his name,

00:06:39.520 --> 00:06:43.270
Hegseth.

00:06:45.120 --> 00:06:48.390
They're going to bring out more troops, which isn't

00:06:48.390 --> 00:06:48.400
a coincidence,

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:51.749
thank God,

00:06:51.759 --> 00:06:53.670
because of what I've seen concerning the

00:06:53.670 --> 00:06:53.680
tree-lighting

00:06:53.680 --> 00:06:56.950
ceremony.

00:06:56.960 --> 00:06:58.950
Whenever I've told you about the map

00:06:58.950 --> 00:06:58.960
with

00:06:58.960 --> 00:07:00.469
the

00:07:00.469 --> 00:07:00.479
Lego-like

00:07:00.479 --> 00:07:03.029
buildings,

00:07:03.039 --> 00:07:05.350
they were planning and

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:07.270
strategizing against our nation's

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:10.150
capital. I saw these men, and

00:07:10.160 --> 00:07:12.710
it was for the underground chatter.

00:07:12.720 --> 00:07:16.629
I keep seeing these secret networks of

00:07:16.639 --> 00:07:19.189
phone lines that

00:07:19.189 --> 00:07:19.199
are

00:07:19.199 --> 00:07:21.110
coded so they can talk

00:07:21.120 --> 00:07:23.510
without being interrupted. I believe

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:26.790
it's the same thing they had in New York

00:07:26.800 --> 00:07:30.070
that we discovered

00:07:30.080 --> 00:07:32.390
around

00:07:32.400 --> 00:07:33.909
September 21st.

00:07:37.599 --> 00:07:41.270
The Lord said Chicago, Seattle,

00:07:41.270 --> 00:07:41.280
and

00:07:41.280 --> 00:07:42.870
Boston

00:07:42.880 --> 00:07:45.029
have

00:07:45.039 --> 00:07:46.550
the same kind of

00:07:46.560 --> 00:07:50.070
networking

00:07:50.070 --> 00:07:50.080
as

00:07:50.080 --> 00:07:53.110
New York. We pray that those be

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:55.830
uncovered and brought to

00:07:55.840 --> 00:07:57.990
light. The Lord

00:07:58.000 --> 00:07:59.430
said these are the same kind of SIM

00:07:59.430 --> 00:07:59.440
cards—a

00:07:59.440 --> 00:08:02.469
very

00:08:02.469 --> 00:08:02.479
well-funded

00:08:02.479 --> 00:08:04.150
thing to

00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:04.160
topple

00:08:04.160 --> 00:08:07.510
the eagle so that

00:08:07.520 --> 00:08:09.749
they are able to do what they want to

00:08:09.759 --> 00:08:12.230
do. They said, 'We must topple the

00:08:12.240 --> 00:08:16.070
eagle and bring havoc on the inside

00:08:16.080 --> 00:08:19.110
so

00:08:19.110 --> 00:08:19.120
we

00:08:19.120 --> 00:08:20.869
can do

00:08:20.879 --> 00:08:22.150
what we want with Israel

00:08:22.150 --> 00:08:22.160
and

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:23.909
these other

00:08:23.909 --> 00:08:23.919
areas.'As

00:08:23.919 --> 00:08:26.390
America goes, so does the world;

00:08:26.400 --> 00:08:27.589
we're the

00:08:27.589 --> 00:08:27.599
watchdogs

00:08:27.599 --> 00:08:29.189
of the world.

00:08:29.199 --> 00:08:30.950
Even now,

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:35.430
the main vision I

00:08:35.440 --> 00:08:38.550
saw for 2025 was Trump coming on the

00:08:38.560 --> 00:08:42.389
scene in January and standing on a

00:08:42.399 --> 00:08:45.110
conductor's platform like

00:08:45.120 --> 00:08:47.670
a lion

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:50.310
tamer, cracking his whip to

00:08:50.320 --> 00:08:52.070
the nations.

00:08:57.040 --> 00:08:59.829
I saw him

00:08:59.839 --> 00:09:02.630
crack his whip at the bear and

00:09:02.640 --> 00:09:04.550
the dragon, and they paused.

00:09:09.519 --> 00:09:11.110
He was

00:09:11.120 --> 00:09:13.190
bringing peace

00:09:13.200 --> 00:09:16.949
for a season, while

00:09:16.949 --> 00:09:16.959
others

00:09:16.959 --> 00:09:18.630
would try to escalate

00:09:18.640 --> 00:09:21.590
things

00:09:21.590 --> 00:09:21.600
and

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.389
maneuver around his

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:27.030
administration, waiting

00:09:27.040 --> 00:09:29.590
for his term to

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:32.230
be over, even

00:09:32.230 --> 00:09:32.240
considering

00:09:32.240 --> 00:09:33.829
how they could eliminate

00:09:33.829 --> 00:09:33.839
him.

00:09:33.839 --> 00:09:36.710
And the Lord said, "We must pray

00:09:36.720 --> 00:09:39.750
for President Trump, not just for the

00:09:39.760 --> 00:09:42.949
physical, but for discernment on who

00:09:42.959 --> 00:09:45.750
he allows into his inner circle as

00:09:45.760 --> 00:09:48.949
nations would try to deceive him."He

00:09:48.949 --> 00:09:48.959
said

00:09:48.959 --> 00:09:50.870
that he would have great discernment in

00:09:50.880 --> 00:09:54.081
the days ahead of how to handle

00:09:56.959 --> 00:09:59.509
doing business.

00:09:59.519 --> 00:10:01.590
"Don't trust everybody."And the Lord said

00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:05.110
he needs to work on discernment.

00:10:05.120 --> 00:10:07.590
Even then, don't just trust people

00:10:07.600 --> 00:10:10.550
blindly, sir. There are enemies; there

00:10:10.560 --> 00:10:13.350
are rats within. And the Lord keeps

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:15.829
telling me there's rats in the Pentagon.

00:10:15.839 --> 00:10:18.069
There's rats in the FBI. There's rats in

00:10:18.079 --> 00:10:20.310
Homeland Security. There's rats in these places.

00:10:20.310 --> 00:10:20.320
And

00:10:20.320 --> 00:10:22.230
he said these people are

00:10:22.240 --> 00:10:24.470
leaking information.

00:10:24.480 --> 00:10:26.870
He specifically told me this. Now, I

00:10:26.880 --> 00:10:28.150
don't know if you have found them all

00:10:28.160 --> 00:10:31.030
yet, but I have prayed continually that

00:10:31.040 --> 00:10:34.310
you will. I even saw in particular

00:10:34.310 --> 00:10:34.320
people—the

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:36.790
Lord showed me these people

00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:39.430
are rats. You must pray for them to be

00:10:39.440 --> 00:10:42.230
exposed and brought to justice. So

00:10:42.240 --> 00:10:43.509
that's been our prayer. As a

00:10:43.519 --> 00:10:44.870
family, we pray over that too. And we

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:47.110
pray over President Trump

00:10:47.110 --> 00:10:47.120
continually—about

00:10:47.120 --> 00:10:49.910
his heart, about his

00:10:49.910 --> 00:10:49.920
veins—even

00:10:49.920 --> 00:10:51.350
before anything was brought up on the

00:10:51.360 --> 00:10:53.990
news. If you go back, we've been

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:56.389
praying over his heart, his veins, and his

00:10:56.399 --> 00:10:59.030
mind for pressure from all the

00:10:59.040 --> 00:11:01.030
stress from the job. It's a

00:11:01.030 --> 00:11:01.040
majorly

00:11:01.040 --> 00:11:03.110
stressful job when you're doing what

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:04.550
he's doing. So, we're praying for him

00:11:04.550 --> 00:11:04.560
and

00:11:04.560 --> 00:11:05.990
we continue to do that. I'm praying

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.990
for his marriage, praying for his kids

00:11:08.000 --> 00:11:11.030
and his grandkids, for Kai in particular

00:11:11.040 --> 00:11:14.150
concerning Washington DC

00:11:14.160 --> 00:11:16.790
when she's there. Praying for her, a

00:11:16.800 --> 00:11:18.949
hedge around and about her. And so, I

00:11:18.959 --> 00:11:21.110
believe with all my heart our prayers

00:11:21.110 --> 00:11:21.120
have

00:11:21.120 --> 00:11:23.670
great

00:11:23.680 --> 00:11:25.670
traction in them and we're making

00:11:25.680 --> 00:11:28.069
progress. So, we're going to continue to

00:11:28.079 --> 00:11:30.710
do that. Let's go over a little

00:11:30.720 --> 00:11:33.670
bit of what happened last night.

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:35.670
If you were here for the almost

00:11:35.680 --> 00:11:38.230
three-hour video—I told Diana, I said,

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:40.710
"Well, the squawkers will squawk, but

00:11:40.720 --> 00:11:42.310
I tell you, the glory was here, and

00:11:44.560 --> 00:11:46.949
I didn't want to cut it

00:11:46.949 --> 00:11:46.959
off."I

00:11:46.959 --> 00:11:48.550
told her, I said, "When I was seeing

00:11:48.560 --> 00:11:51.829
over there and that angel came,

00:11:51.839 --> 00:11:53.948
that was

00:11:53.958 --> 00:11:54.069
beautiful."When

00:11:54.079 --> 00:11:55.269
you have those

00:11:55.279 --> 00:11:57.910
experiences with the Father...

00:11:57.920 --> 00:11:59.750
She's been crying. I'm telling you, the

00:11:59.760 --> 00:12:01.829
glory of the Lord—we felt it today. And

00:12:01.839 --> 00:12:04.069
when the angel said to us,

00:12:04.079 --> 00:12:06.230
"I've been assigned

00:12:06.240 --> 00:12:09.110
to you. I have been

00:12:09.110 --> 00:12:09.120
assigned."Diana

00:12:09.120 --> 00:12:11.030
and

00:12:11.040 --> 00:12:14.253
I—Diana's

00:12:14.253 --> 00:12:14.263
a

00:12:14.263 --> 00:12:14.870
thinker—were

00:12:14.880 --> 00:12:18.069
just going over things: Is it

00:12:18.079 --> 00:12:20.150
Michael? Was that Michael? He didn't say

00:12:20.160 --> 00:12:22.870
his name. I don't know. But I believe he

00:12:22.880 --> 00:12:25.110
was an archangel. And he said, "I have

00:12:25.120 --> 00:12:26.389
been assigned to help you. I've been

00:12:26.389 --> 00:12:26.399
assigned."And

00:12:26.399 --> 00:12:29.030
when he was standing

